Package com.kwant.excelandcsvtojson.util

Class ExcelCSVConverter

java.lang.Object
com.kwant.excelandcsvtojson.util.ExcelCSVConverter
@Service public class ExcelCSVConverter extends Object
This is a Core class that has the main logic to convert the excel to Json and CSV. Also, CSV to JSON is also implemented. Both Functions consuming file with file input and input stream is done.
